com.mcoe.common.framework

Class ElementInspector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mcoe.common.framework.ElementInspector
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericExecutor

    public class ElementInspector
extends java.lang.Object
    This class helps to inspect elements using WebDriver. This class is responsible for creating driver using DriverProvider.

    Created by ksoni on 01/05/18.
